channel.title: Typography ideas
channel.description:
I need some help guys, give me some ideas. It needs to be very simplistic, and minimalistic. If you have any ideas on a color palette, tell me. And ideas on how to present it. All I want to say is 'The Siege youth ministry' in that exact format. I've had a couple ideas I've been playing with. I had done them originally, and then had a friend edit them and try his hand at it. So they really don't look exactly like this. They look better.
